summary: A whole new city brought back up from the sea...
descriptionHtml:
This mod currently adds the entire city of Winterhold, including a player house, new, voiced NPCs, and much more! I plan to do a quest involving raising it from the sea, so keep with the mod until I do finish that part.

Features:
================
- New NPCs with voice acting
- The entire city of Winterhold rebuilt and thriving again
- New dungeons to explore*
- Side quests involving the new city and NPCs*
- Much more!
*Still have lots of work to do on these parts, bear with me until I finish them!
author: VirtualWeasel and Duruza
